snippet.title: Need for Speed: Hot Pursuit Challenges - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
--- Rule Urban Tropics and Win The Grand Marathon ---

Need for Speed: Hot Pursuit Challenges is a NFS Hot Pursuit 2 fan continuation for NFS Most Wanted (2005).
This is a cinematic launch trailer, which is supposed to engage you into the project.

OUT NOW - Download at links down below:
* Download page on official website: https://sites.google.com/view/hot-pursuit-challenges/download
* NFSMods page: https://nfsmods.xyz/mod/3280

Find out more at:
* Official website (To get to know the project): https://sites.google.com/view/hot-pursuit-challenges
* Discord server (For News, Contests and many other stuff!): https://discord.gg/DMKFxAv

Music used:
* Hot Action Cop - Going Down On It (Instrumental Remix)

Project by elaymm4 (aka Laymer), 2018-2021.
All rights for original game are reserved to Electronic Arts Inc.
